{# Formal response frame template
   Used by draft-generator when tone=formal.
   Variables:
     sender_display_name — recipient's display name (may be empty)
     user_display_name   — current user's display name
     original_subject    — original email subject
     priority            — P0|P1|P2|P3
     draft_body          — LLM-generated body text
     scheduling_request  — true|false
     proposed_times      — list of extracted time strings
#}
Dear {{ sender_display_name | default("Sir/Madam") }},

{% if priority == "P0" %}
Thank you for your urgent message. I am treating this as a high-priority
matter and will ensure it receives immediate attention.

{% elif priority == "P1" %}
Thank you for reaching out. I am prioritizing your message and will respond
in full within four business hours.

{% endif %}
{{ draft_body }}

{% if scheduling_request and proposed_times | length > 0 %}
Regarding the scheduling request in your message: the following times
were noted as potential options — {{ proposed_times | join(", ") }}.
Please let me know which works best for you, or suggest an alternative.

{% endif %}
Best regards,
{{ user_display_name }}

---
*Draft generated by xiaoguai email-triage v{{ pack_version }}.*
*Priority: {{ priority }} · Sender class: {{ sender_class }}*
